profile_positions.description:
Manage a team of Account Managers and Account Coordinators in the Cape Town Office that cover 4 provinces in South Africa.
Direct account management for specific hotels in the KwaZulu-Natal, Eastern Cape, Free State, Northern Cape and previously the Greater Western Cape.
Market Visits to priority cities and hotels
Responsible for area coverage;
Support Booking.com BV’s-strategy for hotel availability and supply within Western Cape
Promote the Booking.com BV brand name and its online reservation services to hotels;
Liaison person for hotels to contact when they have questions;
Providing hotels with information and advice by mail and email, including follow-ups;
Accompany and train hotels on how to use Booking.com’s extranet and rates & availability system;
Support hotels with regards to Booking.com’s system;
Inform hotels and advise on allotment, availability and supply;
Organize and coordinate Tourist Trade Fair visits to liaise with hotels;
Versatility and adaption to the latest guidelines from Booking.com BV.
Internal Tool Super User for the African Continent (covering 7 offices)
Construction, Implementation and Execution of large scale projects across Southern Africa Region
Reporting Line function for team members (recruitment, HR, administration, performance management, appraisal delivery and feedback, mentoring and coaching)
